{
  "title": "Indulgent Indian Tiger Prawns Rasam",
  "description": "A rich and flavorful Hyderabadi dish featuring succulent tiger prawns in a spicy rasam broth, infused with aromatic oils and served in a traditional tajine clay vessel.",
  "cuisine": "Indian",
